目前待辦公文查詢是 MOCK JSON，語法放在 todo_mock.json 的 sql_example.query，內容如下：

SELECT TOP 100 TM.TM_GRSNO, TM.TM_DATE, TM.TM_RSTP, TM.TM_SUBJ, TM.TM_PSID, TM.TM_NAME, TD.TD_SUBJ, TD.TD_PATH
FROM mnda.dbo.DCS3_TRST_MST TM
LEFT JOIN mnda.dbo.DCS3_TRST_DAT TD ON TM.TM_SNO = TD.TD_SNO
WHERE TM.TM_PSID = :login_user
  AND (TM.TM_GRSNO LIKE :q OR TM.TM_SUBJ LIKE :q)
ORDER BY TM.TM_DATE DESC